quran[7{c,v,t}:
9,100,"woh mohajir o Ansar jinhon ne sab se pehlay dawat imaan par labaik kehnay mein Sabqat ki, neez woh jo baad meinrasbaazی ke sath peechay aeye, Allah un se raazi howa aur woh Allah se raazi hue, Allah ne un ke liye aisay baagh muhayya kar rakhay hain jin ke neechay nhrin behti hon gi aur woh un mein hamesha rahen ge, yahi azeem al shan kamyabi hai"
9,101,"tumahray gird o paish jo badwi rehtay hain un mein bohat se munafiq hain aur isi terhan khud madinah ke bashindon mein bhi munafiq mojood hain jo nifaq mein taaq ho gay hain tum inhen nahi jantay, hum un ko jantay hain qareeb hai woh waqt jab hum un ko dohri saza den ge, phir woh ziyada barri saza ke liye wapas laaye jayen ge"
9,102,"kuch aur log hain jinhon ne apneKasoroo-n ka aitraaf kar liya hai un ka amal makhloot hai, kuch naik hai aur kuch bad, baeed nahi ke Allah un par phir meharban ho jaye kyunkay woh dar guzar karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
9,103,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum un ke amwal mein se sadqa le kar inhen pak karo aur ( neki ki raah mein ) inhen barhao, aur un ke haq mein duaye rehmat karo kyunkay tumhari dua un ke liye wajah taskeen hogi, Allah sab kuch santa aur jaanta hai"
9,104,"kya inn logon ko maloom nahi hai ke woh Allah hi hai jo apne bundon ki tauba qubool karta hai aur un ki khairaat ko qabuliat ataa farmata hai, aur yeh ke Allah bohat maaf karne wala aur Raheem hai ?"
9,105,"aur ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn logon se kehdo ke tum amal karo, Allah aur is ka rasool aur momnin sab dekhen ge ke tumhara tarz amal ab kya rehta hai phir tum uss ki taraf palta-ayjao ge jo khulay aur chupay sab ko jaanta hai aur woh tumhe bta day ga ke tum kya karte rahay ho"
9,106,"kuch Dosar y log hain jin ka maamla abhi khuda ke hukum partehra howa hai, chahay inhen saza day aur chahay unn par az sir no meharban ho jaye Allah sab kuch jaanta hai aur hakeem o Dana hai"
